org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.refsem

Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • TOP
      • org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.refsem.Element
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Attribute, Date, Entity, Event, Time

    public class Element
extends TOP
    A basic semantic unit that refers to something in the real world, including Entities, Events, Attributes, Dates. Element inherits from uima.cas.TOP to combine textual mentions of these real-world objects. Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015 XML source: /Users/pei/workspace/apache-ctakes/3.2.2/ctakes-ytex-uima/target/jcasgen/typesystem.xml
